by nicolas-grekas at 2015-09-10T08:52:34Z

Thanks for the fix. I'd prefer we don't use any global variable. I suggest instead using a single function:
```php
function with_clock_mock($enable = null)
{
    static $enabled;

    if (null === $enable) {
        return $enabled;
    }

    $enabled = $enable;
}
```

